title: Surprise Announcement and Gift Arrival
author: MaryGirl Moody

And experts in horror- you were my first ever subscription, and ask a mortician is the most recent. Kindred spirits methinks.
Love u, Mary. So proud of you
Mary you should contact Shane Dawson and make a Short horror film together !
I went to the hot topic at the mall today 😂
I can probably help solved crimes. With u. It's part of my gift. Impath, Medium, all sorts.
